main event: A pair of observers saw an unidentified long flame-like object while driving along a highway on November 17, 1965.
interesting points: The object was described as a long flame approximately 33 feet in length,The observers saw the object from the windshield of their car while driving,The object was flying parallel to the ground and disappeared over the horizon after 5 to 10 seconds, The sighting occurred around 2353 Zulu time during the night, and visibility conditions were reported as clear and excellent.
witness description: one male observer and his wife, both total abstainers and reported to be sober and reasonable
